- cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) is relevant as the problem involves coloring and partitioning a discrete structure. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is relevant as the problem involves finding a solution that satisfies certain constraints. 
- cs.CC (Computational Complexity) is less likely but still possible as the paper discusses the complexity of the painting and shows that there exists a painting with bounded complexity per cell.
